HEADWORD: Micrurus
<hw>Micrurus</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A genus of snakes including
certain of the coral snakes, such as the <member>eastern coral
snake</member> (<spn>Micrurus fulvius</spn>).</def>⟦br⟧
